Nature Photography - Stream in Autumn Woods by Jack Hollingsworth

Buy this print on Art.com: http://go.art.com/Vc4amFC

Where are your favorite fall haunts? Do you have a favorite spot to stroll and take in the beauty of the season? We wish we could transport ourselves right into the middle of this crisp autumn afternoon captured by Jack Hollingsworth. There’s something so beautiful and serene about a babbling creek running through the color riot of the fall foliage.

Jack Hollingsworth is a lifestyle, portrait, and travel photographer who works out of Austin, Texas. His clients include Four Seasons Hotel, Ritz Carlton, Star Clippers, American Airlines, and many tourism agencies. In addition to his credentials as a photographer, Hollingsworth is one of the most active contemporary photographers on Twitter! He offers advice on anything from social media strategy for photographers, to how to get the best pictures with your camera phone.

Explore Jack Hollingsworth’s travels in our gallery of his work: http://www.art.com/gallery/id--a41584/jack-hollingsworth-posters.htm?rfid=978544
